  <abstract role="description-short">
    <para>This collection provides expert tips for using Java-based utilities
    from projects such as Apache Commons, Apache Lucene, and Apache Velocity.
    You don't have to be an expert, the book's solution-based format contains
    code examples for a wide variety of web, XML, network, testing, and
    application projects. If you want to learn how to combine common
    open-source Java utilities to create powerful Java applications and tools,
    the <emphasis>${book.title}</emphasis> is for you.</para>
  </abstract>

